# Build context is .devcontainer/. Only these are COPY'd into the image:
#   init-firewall.sh, perms-fix.sh, entrypoint.sh, squid.conf, allowlist.txt
# Everything below is used on the host or at runtime (bind-mounted), not in the
# build — keep it out of the daemon build context.
# NOTE: list host-only bin/ files EXPLICITLY (not `bin/` + `!bin/verify-pins`).
# apple/container's build-context differ mis-orders re-included paths and aborts
# with `changes out of order`. Explicit excludes avoid it; identical under Docker.
README.md
bin/agent
bin/claude
bin/doctor
launcher-common.sh
features/
devcontainer.json
devcontainer-lock.json
.dockerignore
